@startuml Vault-KeyManagement
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #0b0b14
skinparam defaultFontColor #e2e8f0
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #6366f1
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #6366f1
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontColor #e2e8f0
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #818cf8
skinparam noteBorderColor #6366f1
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam noteFontColor #e2e8f0

title Vault - API Key CRUD 与数据流

actor 用户
participant "MainScreen\n卡片 UI" as UI
participant "app.js" as App
participant "CryptoModule (C)" as Crypto
participant "StorageModule (S)" as Storage

== 添加 API Key ==

用户 -> UI : 点击 + 按钮
UI -> App : openAdd()
App -> UI : 显示弹窗 (供应商快速选择)

用户 -> UI : 填写名称/Key/URL/备注
用户 -> UI : 点击保存
UI -> App : saveKey(event)

App -> App : 验证 (名称和Key不为空)

App -> App : keys.push({id: uuid(), name, apiKey, url, notes, createdAt, updatedAt})

loop 每个 key in keys
    App -> Crypto : enc(key.apiKey, mk)
    Crypto --> App : {ciphertext, iv} (AES-256-GCM)
end

App -> Storage : saveData(storedKeys[])
Storage -> Storage : localStorage.setItem('vault_data', JSON)

App -> UI : renderKeys() 刷新卡片
App -> UI : toast('已添加')

== 编辑 API Key ==

用户 -> UI : 点击编辑按钮
UI -> App : openEdit(id)
App -> App : 查找 keys 数组
App -> UI : 填充弹窗表单

用户 -> UI : 修改内容
UI -> App : saveKey(event)
App -> App : 更新 keys 数组
App -> App : saveAll() 重新加密存储
App -> UI : renderKeys() + toast('已更新')

== 删除 API Key ==

用户 -> UI : 点击删除按钮
UI -> App : delKey(id)
App -> UI : confirm('确定删除？')
用户 -> UI : 确认
App -> App : keys.filter(k => k.id !== id)
App -> App : saveAll() 重新加密存储
App -> UI : renderKeys() + toast('已删除')

== 搜索过滤 ==

用户 -> UI : 输入搜索关键词
UI -> App : renderKeys()
App -> App : keys.filter(k => name/url/notes 包含关键词)
App -> UI : 渲染过滤后的卡片

== 导出 Excel ==

用户 -> UI : 点击"导出 Excel"
UI -> App : exportAllExcel()
App -> App : 构造 data[] 明文数据
App -> App : XLSX.utils.json_to_sheet(data)
App -> App : XLSX.writeFile(wb, 'vault_export_时间戳.xlsx')

@enduml
